The paper discusses the security and privacy threats in IoT, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the challenges in current research, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the social applications of IoT, which could be related to social and information networks (cs.SI) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
